## 🌐 TNetwork
# 📄 Overview
Welcome to our TNetWork application! Our platform aims to connect people from around the world in a safe and engaging environment. Whether you're here to share your thoughts, connect with friends, or discover new communities, we're thrilled to have you join us.

Feature List:

-   🌟 Tech stack: MERN + Socket.io + Chakra UI 
-   🔐 Authentication & Authorization with JWT (Asymmetric encryption, Handle refreshtoken,...)
-   📝 Create Post
-   🗑️ Delete Post
-   🔔 RealTime Notifications
-   🔊 Notification sounds
-   📞 Video Calling
-   ❤️ Like/Unlike Post
-   💬 Comment to a Post
-   👥 Follow/Unfollow Users
-   👥 Suggested Users to Follow
-   📝 Edit Profile Info and Profile Image
-   ❄️ Freeze Your Account
-   💬 Chat App With Image Support
-   👀 Seen/Unseen Status for Messages
-   ⏳ And much more!

### Setup .env file

```js
PORT=...
PRO_DB_HOST=localhost
PRO_DB_PORT=27017
PRO_DB_NAME=...
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=...
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=...
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=...
```

### Build the app

```shell
npm run build
```

### Start the app

```shell
npm start
```
